sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as JS Frontend (Client)
    participant FILE as FileReader (Data)
    participant ORCH as app.py (Orchestrator)
    participant FACT as TranslatorFactory
    participant STRAT as AWS Strategy
    participant AWS as Amazon Translate (Cloud)

    Note over UI, AWS: User Refreshes Webpage (Horizontal Flow)

    UI->>ORCH: GET /headlines
    activate ORCH

    ORCH->>FILE: read_headlines("headline_edwin.txt")
    activate FILE
    FILE-->>ORCH: List of raw strings
    deactivate FILE

    ORCH->>FACT: get_translator("AWS")
    activate FACT
    FACT-->>ORCH: AWSTranslator Instance
    deactivate FACT

    loop For each headline
        ORCH->>STRAT: translate(text)
        activate STRAT
        STRAT->>AWS: Post Translation Request
        AWS-->>STRAT: Translated JSON Result
        STRAT-->>ORCH: Success or "Not Supported"
        deactivate STRAT
    end

    ORCH-->>UI: Final Aggregated JSON Data
    deactivate ORCH

    Note over UI: JS UI_Renderer updates HTML Table